This is great news, but last time I checked, the European Commission on Humane Rights does not recognize abortion as a human right, unless of course, you’re the UN or the African women I heard of last week, who sauntered around Dubai and who said they believe all girls should be allowed to have abortions in place of school, so they can sleep with men for money – they called it poverty doing funny things to them. As if that weren’t an invasion of human rights as I can tell you for a massive fact that not all girls end up on the streets.Rwanda
